Cream cheese lemon cake is what we call, Sunshine served on a platter. With a preparation time of only 20 minutes and a cooking time of 55 minutes, your cream cheese lemon cake will be ready within 2 hrs. Ingredients Preparation Step 1 Preheat the oven to moderate heat 170 â€“ 150 degrees. Grease the baking pan. Step 2 In a bowl, beat all the ingredients in an electric mixer on low speed until all is combined. Step 3 Beat until all the mixture is smooth and changed colour. Step 4 Spread the mixture into a prepared pan, then bake for 55 minutes. Step 5 Remove from oven and cool on a rack. Dust the cake with icing sugar and store in the fridge (optional)